Task 2
- Compilation
	gcc -o task2_spoofer task2_spoofer.c
- Executing the program

	sudo task2_spoofer <option #>

	Options:
		1: ICMP Echo Request
		2: Ethernet Frame

Task 3
- Compilation
	gcc -o task3_sniff_snoop task3_sniff_snoop.c -lpcap
- Executing the program
	
	sudo ./task3_sniff_snoop <interface name>

	Interface name e.g. eth0 or eth14
- According to my VMs setup, machine A has IP 192.168.15.5 and machine B has IP 
	192.168.15.4. Please do not change these two in the program.
